ian province of Westphalia.", "extract_html": "<p><b>Westfalenstadion</b> is a football stadium in Dortmund, North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany, which is the home stadium of Borussia Dortmund. Officially called <b>Signal Iduna Park</b> for sponsorship reasons and <b>BVB Stadion Dortmund</b> in UEFA competitions, the name derives from the former Prussian province of Westphalia.</p>"}